snippet.title: Gameplay Preview | The Pirate Mermaid Otome
snippet.description:
Try the demo: https://navigame.itch.io/the-pirate-mermaid

Some in-game clips from our upcoming fantasy otome visual novel "The Pirate Mermaid."

Follow our dev blog for the latest updates: http://navigame-media.tumblr.com/

Song by Souichi Sakagami: http://tandess.com/en/music/
